 291:SynaptiX_FDK/app/user/sx_mqtt/sx_user_mqtt.c **** /*
 292:SynaptiX_FDK/app/user/sx_mqtt/sx_user_mqtt.c ****  * Stop the MQTT service and wait for it to actually disconnect.
 293:SynaptiX_FDK/app/user/sx_mqtt/sx_user_mqtt.c ****  *
 294:SynaptiX_FDK/app/user/sx_mqtt/sx_user_mqtt.c ****  * NOTE: this remains a blocking busy-wait loop, unlike the rest of this
 295:SynaptiX_FDK/app/user/sx_mqtt/sx_user_mqtt.c ****  * architecture which is non-blocking/poll-based — kept as-is, not something
 296:SynaptiX_FDK/app/user/sx_mqtt/sx_user_mqtt.c ****  * this refactor changes on its own initiative. sx_mqtt_disconnect() already
ARM GAS  C:\Users\DELL\AppData\Local\Temp\cctQ8jJB.s 			page 47


 297:SynaptiX_FDK/app/user/sx_mqtt/sx_user_mqtt.c ****  * goes through modem_ops_t.mqtt_disconnect() -> the driver's own
 298:SynaptiX_FDK/app/user/sx_mqtt/sx_user_mqtt.c ****  * CMQTTDISC/CMQTTREL/CMQTTSTOP sequence (see a7677s_mqtt_state_t's DISC/
 299:SynaptiX_FDK/app/user/sx_mqtt/sx_user_mqtt.c ****  * REL/STOP states) and reports completion asynchronously via sx_mqtt_t's
 300:SynaptiX_FDK/app/user/sx_mqtt/sx_user_mqtt.c ****  * state flipping to SX_MQTT_STATE_DISCONNECTED. There is no separate
 301:SynaptiX_FDK/app/user/sx_mqtt/sx_user_mqtt.c ****  * "mqtt_stop" operation in modem_ops_t (confirmed with the user:
 302:SynaptiX_FDK/app/user/sx_mqtt/sx_user_mqtt.c ****  * sx_mqtt_disconnect() alone replaces the old two-call
 303:SynaptiX_FDK/app/user/sx_mqtt/sx_user_mqtt.c ****  * sim76xx_mqtt_disconnect()+sim76xx_mqtt_stop() sequence). This function
 304:SynaptiX_FDK/app/user/sx_mqtt/sx_user_mqtt.c ****  * polls sx_mqtt_t.state directly instead of relying on a raw AT command
 305:SynaptiX_FDK/app/user/sx_mqtt/sx_user_mqtt.c ****  * callback — cb_mqtt_stop_done/cb_mqtt_disc_done and the modem_t-typed
 306:SynaptiX_FDK/app/user/sx_mqtt/sx_user_mqtt.c ****  * callback signature they used are gone, since modem_ops_t's mqtt_cb_t is
 307:SynaptiX_FDK/app/user/sx_mqtt/sx_user_mqtt.c ****  * the only callback shape available now.
 308:SynaptiX_FDK/app/user/sx_mqtt/sx_user_mqtt.c ****  */
